OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FIn the wilds of Australia's
OL,7,     FNorthern Territory, 24-year-old
OL,8,     Ftrucker Boe Vella crosses
OL,9,     Fcrocodile infested rivers to
OL,10,     Fdeliver desperately needed goods
OL,11,     Fbefore the wet season hits.
